data.title: Woodburn, OR - Portland Airport (PDX)
data.meta_description: Airport transportation between Woodburn, OR - Portland International Airport (PDX) including transit, scheduled service, shuttle, taxi, limo, and charter bus service.
data.text: If your company or organization offers transportation services between the City of Woodburn located in the Marion County in the state of Oregon and the Portland International Airport (PDX), you can list your rates here for free. We accept rates for all ground transportation services including public transit,dial a ride, fixed route, airport shuttle, taxi, private transportation like limousine and car service,and charter bus airporters. If you offer transfers between Woodburn, OR and Portland Airport and would like to list your offer, please contact us.
